---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const updated = '2026-05-05';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — Yield to Freedom"
  description="Terms governing use of yieldtofreedom.com, operated by Creative Bandit LLC."
>
  <article
    class="max-w-3xl space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 [&_a]:font-semibold [&_a]:text-blue-700 hover:[&_a]:text-blue-900 [&_strong]:font-semibold"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Terms of service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: {updated} (UTC)</p>
    <p>
      These Terms govern your access to and use of <strong>yieldtofreedom.com</strong> (the “Site”), operated by
      <strong>Creative Bandit LLC</strong> (“Company,” “we,” “us”). By using the Site, you agree to these Terms and our
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy policy</a>. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Educational use only</h2>
    <p>
      The Site provides general educational information about ETFs and related concepts. Nothing on the Site is
      personalized investment, tax, or legal advice, and nothing is an offer or solicitation to buy or sell securities.
      ETF metrics and “Yield to Freedom” grades are proprietary research aids based on incomplete or delayed data and may
      contain errors; always verify with official filings and professional advisers before acting.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">No fiduciary relationship</h2>
    <p>
      Using the Site does not create an advisory, fiduciary, or client relationship between you and Creative Bandit LLC.
      Company is not a registered investment adviser unless separately disclosed in writing for a specific offering.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Accounts and eligibility</h2>
    <p>
      Certain future features may require an account or subscription. You agree to provide accurate information and keep
      credentials confidential. You must be legally able to enter contracts in your jurisdiction to register where
      registration is offered.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>You agree not to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
      <li>Misuse the Site or attempt unauthorized access to systems, data, or accounts.</li>
      <li>Use automated means to scrape or overload the Site in violation of robots policies or applicable law.</li>
      <li>Reverse engineer or circumvent technical protections except where prohibited restrictions do not apply.</li>
      <li>Use the Site for unlawful, harassing, or infringing activity.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>
      Site content (including layout, copy, tooling UX, and grading methodology descriptions) is owned by Creative Bandit LLC
      or its licensors except where third-party trademarks apply to ETF names or issuer marks. You receive a limited,
      personal, non-exclusive license to browse and use features we intentionally provide; reproduction beyond fair use or
      copying requires written permission unless expressly permitted on the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Third-party links and data</h2>
    <p>
      The Site may reference third-party tools, brokers, or data vendors. Those parties have their own terms. Company does
      not control third-party sites or guarantee accuracy of vendor-supplied figures displayed on the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
    <p>
      THE SITE AND CONTENT ARE PROVIDED “AS IS” AND “AS AVAILABLE,” WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, WHETHER EXPRESS OR
      IMPLIED, INCLUDING MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, ACCURACY, OR NON-INFRINGEMENT, TO THE MAXIMUM
      EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, CREATIVE BANDIT LLC AND ITS OWNERS, EMPLOYEES, AND AFFILIATES WILL NOT BE
      LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR EXEMPLARY DAMAGES, OR LOST PROFITS OR DATA, ARISING
      OUT OF YOUR USE OF THE SITE, EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY. OUR AGGREGATE LIABILITY FOR ANY CLAIM RELATING TO
      THE SITE WILL NOT EXCEED THE GREATER OF (A) THE AMOUNTS YOU PAID TO COMPANY FOR THE SPECIFIC SERVICE GIVING RISE TO
      THE CLAIM IN THE TWELVE MONTHS BEFORE THE CLAIM OR (B) ONE HUNDRED U.S. DOLLARS ($100).
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Indemnity</h2>
    <p>
      You will defend and indemnify Creative Bandit LLC against claims arising from your misuse of the Site or violation of
      these Terms, subject to applicable law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Termination</h2>
    <p>
      We may suspend or terminate access to the Site or features at any time, with or without notice, particularly for
      abuse or legal compliance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Governing law</h2>
    <p>
      These Terms are governed by the laws of the United States and the State of Delaware, excluding conflict-of-law rules,
      unless mandatory consumer protections in your jurisdiction provide otherwise.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may modify these Terms by posting updates on this page and revising the “Last updated” date. Continued use after
      changes become effective constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms for non-material updates where permitted by law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Legal notices or general inquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@yieldtofreedom.com">hello@yieldtofreedom.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="pt-4"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
  </article>
</Base>
